description: Forbid Next.js and SSR frameworks in EduNudg
alwaysApply: true
---

# No Next.js

EduNudg uses **Vite + React SPA** only.

## Forbidden

- `next`, `next/router`, `next/navigation`, App Router, `getServerSideProps`, `getStaticProps`
- React Server Components, `"use server"` in app code
- Remix, Gatsby for this repo

## Required

- `apps/web` — Vite + React Router
- Server logic — Supabase RLS, triggers, Edge Functions in `supabase/functions/`

If you need API endpoints, use Supabase Edge Functions, not Next.js API routes.
